<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">
Dear EverQuest community.<P>I know you english folk love yer language, but French also like their own.<P>From name, to "surname", also in the way some people talk, you can know they are French. I play on Erolisi Marr and i know at least 50 French people.<P>On Karanas, more than the Quarter speak French. We've come to a point where the service for the French is inadequate. Imagine, we're paying, we could at least  get a protoype server, i dont want a server where even the npc speak French, but a server where the /ooc and everything would be in French, a server where the /petition could be in French. I myself propose myself as a guide on this server. Just think about it, we're maybe minority, but were here, and at more, were paying. So take a look at this please, thank you.<P><BR>Mayasej everbuzz<P>P.S: I  have over 10 month of playing capabilties, a character over level 50 and have a well known reputation, and each days, im making new French friends on a server i tought i knew.   <IMG SRC="biggrin.gif" border="0"><P>--------------------<P>Mess iss betterss than ye
</FONT>
