Not that we are stubborn or anything...<P><BR>It's called Cultural identification...<P><BR>French is the diplomatic language, English business language, why diplomatic language as French ?<P>Because they're at least 100 way to say the same things.<P>Also, I would like to add: English may be the universal language, but when you travel, you always feel better talking with the inhabittant in their language, so from now on, il stop my debate, because I love French, from now on Il stop asking English to tell French were not the same kind of people, from now on Il stop believing into a brotherhood of man, distinguished with cultural identification such as their language.<P>From now on, il stop dreaming about a totaly free french server that wouldn't hurt English user's, since they already have their own.<P><BR>Mayasej Everbuzz<P><BR>  Je sais que c'est dur le Francais, mais c'est si beau, si parfait!<P>Apprenez le, et etendez la langue à toute la planète!<P>--------------------<P>Mess iss betterss than ye
